data.description: Sitting on over 3 acres that backs up to Beaverdam is where you will find this gem.  This house features an open concept, 3 bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms, and a vaulted ceiling in the living room.  The walls and ceiling has a fresh coat of paint and is ready for your touch.  That is just on the inside.  The patio will be a great place for you to sit and enjoy the nature that surrounds this park like property.  Plenty of covered areas to keep your toys and lawn equipment.  Just a short walk to the  back of the property and you are ready to put your canoe or kayak in Beaverdam Reservoir for a stroll on the water.
